  "body": "**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n\r\n1. `npm init -y`\r\n2. `npx hardhat` and select to create a config file\r\n3. `npm i hardhat`\r\n4. `npx hardhat node --fork https://eth-mainnet.alchemyapi.io/v2/<key>` as per https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/guides/mainnet-forking.html#forking-from-mainnet\r\n\r\nOutput: `Error HH604: Error running JSON-RPC server: Expected 'isActivatedEIP' to only be called with 2930 or 1559`\r\n\r\nNever had this error before. I can only assume this is some sort of problem with either the latest Hardhat or the latest Ethereumjs.",
